      "description": "The Horizon Kinetics Texas ETF (TEXX) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in total market equity. The fund seeks long-term capital appreciation by actively managing a narrow portfolio of Texas companies. Security selection focuses on businesses poised to benefit from the long-term economic growth, population expansion, and favorable tax and legal environment in Texas. TEXX was launched on Jan 22, 2026 and is issued by Horizon Kinetics.",
